903
00:56:20,114 --> 00:56:21,274
No, it's common sense.

904
00:56:21,364 --> 00:56:22,604
According to your common sense,

905
00:56:22,694 --> 00:56:25,204
someone who can’t lie can't be a reporter?

906
00:56:29,394 --> 00:56:31,914
Let go of me. I don't need all these.

907
00:56:34,614 --> 00:56:35,694
Yes, that can never happen.

908
00:56:36,474 --> 00:56:39,274
How can you say 'never' so easily?

909
00:56:39,634 --> 00:56:41,704
How can you so easily judge
someone else's life?

910
00:56:41,794 --> 00:56:44,394
