913
00:56:50,609 --> 00:56:51,859
What a joke.

914
00:56:52,299 --> 00:56:54,449
A wolf does not bark at a tiger.

915
00:56:54,849 --> 00:56:56,979
Only foolish and ignorant
mutts would do that.

916
00:56:57,639 --> 00:56:59,399
There's nothing more foolish and feeble

917
00:56:59,659 --> 00:57:01,167
than carelessly barking up the wrong tree.

918
00:57:01,799 --> 00:57:05,109
Do you even know what reporter is...

